Usage: chpldoc [flags] [source files]

Documentation Options:
  -o, --output-dir <dirname>          Sets the documentation directory to
                                      <dirname>
      --author <author>               Documentation author string
      --comment-style <indicator>     Only includes comments that start with
                                      <indicator>
  -M, --module-dir <directory>        Add directory to module search path
      --process-used-modules          Also parse and document 'use'd modules
      --save-sphinx <directory>       Save generated Sphinx project in
                                      directory
      --text-only                     Generate text documentation only
      --[no-]html                     [Don't] generate html documentation (on
                                      by default)
      --index <index>                 Path to the index.rst to use
      --project-name <projectname>    Sets the name of project in the
                                      documentation
      --project-description <projectdescription>
                                      Sets the project description in the
                                      documentation
      --project-version <projectversion>
                                      Sets the documentation version to
                                      <projectversion>
      --project-copyright-year <projectcopyrightyear>
                                      Sets the project copyright year in the
                                      documentation
      --[no-]print-commands           [Don't] print system commands
      --[no-]warn-unknown-attribute-toolname
                                      Enable warnings when an unknown tool
                                      name is found in an attribute
      --using-attribute-toolname <toolname>
                                      Specify additional tool names for
                                      attributes that are expected in the
                                      source

Information Options:
  -h, --help                          Help (show this list)
      --help-env                      Environment variable help
      --help-settings                 Current flag settings
      --version                       Show version
      --copyright                     Show copyright
